Package org.odftoolkit.odfdom.taglet

Class OdfDatatypeTaglet

java.lang.Object
org.odftoolkit.odfdom.taglet.OdfDatatypeTaglet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Taglet
public class OdfDatatypeTaglet extends Object implements Taglet
This class implements a custom taglet to the map the ODF datatype to the declaration of the ODF datatype in the OpenDocument specification.

The position of the OpenDocument specification in HTML can be provided using an environment variable or java system property, while the system property overrides the environment variable. In case nothing is been a default path within the JavaDoc resources directory is being used.

For example the taglet {@odf.datatype countryCode} would be resolved without variable settings to JAVA_DOC_BASE/resources/OpenDocument-v1.2-part1.html#datatype-countryCode.
